        "title": "Add Node to org.w3c.dom.NodeList",
        "body": "<p>How to add a node like<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Element node = (Element) xpath.evaluate(\"//property[@value = 'entryDataTitle']\", doc, XPathConstants.NODE);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>to my org.w3c.dom.NodeList?<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>NodeList entryDataItem = (NodeList) xpath.evaluate(\"//item[@name='entryDataItem']\", doc, XPathConstants.NODESET);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
